PropertySheetDialog
public class BaseDialog
extends javax.swing.JDialog

An extension of the JDialog with built-in support for OK/CANCEL/CLOSE buttons. BaseDialog adds:

  • support for ESCAPE key to dispose the window
  • ok, cancel methods
  • simple method to check if ok or cancel was called (ask())
  • button pane
  • banner pane

See Also:
Serialized Form

Field Detail

OK_CANCEL_DIALOG

public static final int OK_CANCEL_DIALOG
Used to set the mode of the dialog to OK/CANCEL. When in this mode, OK and Cancel buttons are automatically added to the dialog.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

CLOSE_DIALOG

public static final int CLOSE_DIALOG
Used to set the mode of the dialog to OK/CANCEL. When in this mode, a Close button is automatically added to the dialog.
